Padre, the Perl IDE makes it very easy to create a plugin for additional tasks 
To download Padre for Windows or get directions how to install on Linux and Mac visit http://padre.perlide.org/

For the Padre mailing list and IRC channel see http://padre.perlide.org/contact.html

